{"type":"article","id":11157,"title":"【創作】【時事圖片背景封面更新！】品蔥週刊封面設計投稿","uid":1967,"topics":[4521,2744],"contents":"更新1219108｛<br>\n設計了兩張以時事圖片做背景的封面<br>\n用圖片做背景時右上‘品蔥週刊’圖標縮小至全封面約1/3寬以避免過度遮擋圖片<br>\n<br>\n中小新聞封面：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SCqBche.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SCqBche.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SCqBche.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n大新聞封面<br>\n大新聞繼續用中小新聞的規格就顯得有點不夠震撼，因此做了修改，但基本結構還是一樣的<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ulxx2Mr.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ulxx2Mr.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ulxx2Mr.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n圖片都是縮小過的，品蔥用的圖床似乎不能上傳大於1MB的文件，否則就報413錯誤<br>\n<br>\n｝<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n響應<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/11143\">https://pincong.rocks/article/11143</a>，結構還是按照@試問誰還未覺醒在文章首頁貼出的樣本，設計了封面，首頁名言及目錄<br>\n<br>\n封面<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/t9ZicCK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/t9ZicCK.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/t9ZicCK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n名言頁<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bwRA8OI.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bwRA8OI.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bwRA8OI.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n目錄<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7kIRGGF.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7kIRGGF.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7kIRGGF.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\nA4規格，右開，內文主要豎排排版&nbsp; <s>不！打死我也不用東亞文字做橫排！！！</s><br>\n封面圖像來自<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7924\">https://pincong.rocks/article/7924</a><br>\n內容不用在意，用亂數假文佔位置而已<br>\n封面背景可替換為時事圖片<br>\n目錄結構參照@試問誰還未覺醒給出的，不過並沒有全填上去，沒填上去的內容排版以此類推","date":"2019-12-18","agreeCount":29,"discussionCount":0}